Usage: report_voltage_scaling [-help] [<objectListOrCollection>]
                              [-analysis_type {early late}]
                              [-output_file <string>] [-view <string>]

-help                        # Prints out the command usage
<objectListOrCollection>     # Names or a collection of leaf instances
                             # (string, optional)
-analysis_type {early late}  # Specifies whether early or late views have to be
                             # checked for voltage scaling. If unspecified,
                             # only 'late' views are checked. (enum, optional)
-output_file <string>        # output file name (string, optional)
-view <string>               # Specify the name(s) of view(s) to be checked for
                             # voltage scaling. (string, optional)